LatexCommand citep
before "but also see"
key "Beyer:2007xd,Beschta_comment_2011"

\end_inset

.
 This produces a seeming paradox--although numbers of herbivores declined
 dramatically (Figure 1A), the proportion of willow production browsed remained
 consistently high (Figure 2A).
\end_layout

